parameters: The only thing left unexplored is this inner part.

This was supposed to be the Magic Tool Research
Club, right? Chloe was the only member, though.
Please move aside and let me in

【Masamune】This might be the final battle. We can't
redo it anymore, but is that okay?

The final battle can only take place on the third
day or later.
What club is this? Is there something here?

Is this... a magical tool? It's of quite good
quality.
I've never seen anything like this before.
Ah, sorry. I entered without permission.

You're someone I've never seen before. Are you
perhaps interested in joining the club?

No, that's not it. I just transferred here and
wanted to take a look around.

Ah, so you're the rumored transfer student. In
that case, feel free to take a good look around.
So it's become a rumor, huh?

Oh, it's rare to have a transfer student, you
know.

Ah, I'm Chloe Sherry, a first-year student. I'm
the president of the Magic Tools Research Club.

Even though I say president, there's only one
member in the club.
Magic tools... Does that mean you made this?

It's not something surprising. Just by looking at
this pendant, you can tell it has power.
I can feel the magical power too.

That's a water pendant! Just by wearing it, it
helps with water magic!
If you'd like, I can give it to you.

Oh my, it's the first time someone has praised my
magical tool.
Even though I'm making such good things.
Magicians dislike relying on magical tools.

Using magical tools is proof of lacking talent.
Tools other than staffs are unpopular.
Indeed, there are many people with such thoughts.

(But in actual combat, you can't say such things.
If this is distributed to the magic unit, it will
be a significant increase in firepower.)

I think it's a brilliant invention. I'm sure it
will be even more appreciated in the future.
I'm happy... I'm glad I've worked hard until now.

You're the first person to appreciate our
invention! I want to call you big brother!
Well, it's not a big deal.
Of course, you're joining the club, right?

Sorry, but I just started school... I have some
things to take care of.

If that's the case, then I guess there's no
helping it.
Oh, by the way, you can use that device too.

If you put in the ingredients, a magic tool will
be completed on its own.

I wouldn't appreciate it if you underestimated
prodigy Chloe Sherry.

Normally, you have to infuse magic into the
ingredients while synthesizing, but this does it
all automatically.

Of course, I can't make anything too complicated,
but I can make something like that pendant with
the flame.

Since I can also make staffs, please try using the
ingredients if you have them.

Speaking of the Magic Tool Encyclopedia, it's
something my relative wrote.
If you find any others, please pick them up.
I'll be able to make more different things.
You're free to use the magic item creation pot.

Big brother! You can freely use the magic tool
creation device, you know!

Oh, and there's something I want to ask using the
magic tool.
Yes, I want you to ask me anything.
I want to ask if there is any magical tool to escape from the prison
牢屋から脱出できる魔道具がないか聞く

If it's just that much, I have it. If you want it,
I'll give it to you.
You're free to use the magic item creation pot.
